  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the addition of video presentation on conventional informed consent.
      Participants divided two randomly, one group read only conventional informed consent, the
      other video presentation was watched after reading conventional consent.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
